// immediately followed by the registered organization name. This is a
// point-in-time snapshot; the registry changes as blocks are assigned.
//
// This file is large and is imported only where the full map is needed: the
// server-side run() and the golden-vector tests. The client tool component
// lazy-loads it with a dynamic import so the page shell stays light.
// ============================================================================

